{"tid":476032,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[本土EDM創作-巴曲]求分享求comment","createTime":"2017-11-21T15:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T05:12:48.000Z","uid":62027,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c2e7d22a0e9558f97f47b2c586ea0b6d628b0f","tid":476032,"uid":62027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"見呢邊都幾多edm post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 想上黎分享一下小弟同埋朋友一齊創作既EDM, 我地叫巴曲,年頭開始玩,到而家為止出左2首歌.<br />\n都係廣東話edm, 呢2首都係近future bass, 比較chill d, soft d. 黎緊會想做d恆d既同玩多d remix<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 牢中花:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X2nDHAWlEVQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX2nDHAWlEVQ&d=oh0x7qK8nOqAef1Cr4y0bzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2b6bcc77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X2nDHAWlEVQ</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 來世<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lFfnE9RYWuc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlFfnE9RYWuc&d=oh0x7qK8nOqAef1Cr4y0bzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b26d1b00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lFfnE9RYWuc</a><br />\n<br />\n我地目標係將廣東話edm做起黎, 係香港做indie難, 做edm 既indie人更難, 基本上係好少資源同support,<br />\n所以好想巴打絲打們比多d意見我地, 同埋支持一下我地<br />\n<br />\n我地個fb page:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/barcodehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbarcodehk%2F&d=oh0x7qK8nOqAef1Cr4y0bzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=0f3b5414\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/barcodehk/</a>"},{"pid":"4639d2b9ce5a66b6a215751b30d6667a8fafc00a","tid":476032,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:47:10.000Z","msg":"加油，你既朋友介紹過你地既作品比我聽"},{"pid":"944f6758c68d4fe9be0637660caf1a535eada5f7","tid":476032,"uid":62027,"like